"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"馬場飲醉係沙圈嘔"},{"pid":"36004e3e9dca887408e0ae8fddbd1a07cba02f51","tid":2075930,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"梅窩游泳池暫時關閉<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列報告，並於適當時間重複廣播：<br />\n<br />\n  游泳人士請注意：康樂及文化事務署（康文署）今日（八月八日）宣布，由於在離島區梅窩游泳池發現小量嘔吐物，該游泳池現已暫時關閉，以便進行清潔消毒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  游泳池將於今日下午三時四十五重開。<br />\n<br />\n  康文署呼籲泳客顧己及人，合力保持泳池清潔衞生，落水前不要吃得過飽，有需要應先使用洗手間。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月8日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間14時55分"},{"pid":"b22bd42f3541d6c4e9325bebb48ef8815d838222","tid":2075930,"uid":132160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"印度"},{"pid":"e57fbd1d3396de5647e00d487704967b38bb046c","tid":2075930,"uid":29842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"等緊一幅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b49ea6000d15d8e57033f020f4fc38247b7f94","tid":2075930,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f12907872cd4a5299a4eeaae63fa40d087fd5519","tid":2075930,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"十幾年前坐叮叮太chok , 係上層個窗嘔左落下層乘客道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"又話被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b794b2079c993752a52a1b2c69520378ce8bf8d","tid":2075930,"uid":141176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"玩過山車既過程中嘔 條拋物線好撚靚"},{"pid":"8618018b4ebbd8f7a3f1e79fe32767a60d21a952","tid":2075930,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a3b49ea6000d15d8e57033f020f4fc38247b7f94","tid":2075930,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f12907872cd4a5299a4